Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:21.42,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,1220,4000,4800)\pos(720,511.685)}Episode 25
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:21.42,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,1220,4000,4800)\pos(713.864,796.854)}Liu Bei Seeks the Virtuous
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, why have you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was passing through when a child led me to visit your esteemed presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:16.34,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,500,6000,6200)\pos(189.263,380)}Sīmǎ Huī\NStyled: Décāo)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, you shouldn't keep secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here today in order to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:28.97,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,500,5500,5700)\pos(1216.156,418.181)}Liú Bèi\N Styled: Xuándé
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest with you, Liu Biao had me attend a meeting in Xiāngyáng —
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,— but Cai Mao tried to harm me, so I fled them and came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I gathered that from your facial expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard of your great reputation, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why has it to this day you have no foundations of your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fate are ever-changing. That is why I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:04:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}The reason why you haven't yet accomplished your great undertaking —
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318} — is because there are no virtuous sage men around to assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}I may not be able  —
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}But with me are ministers{\i1} Sūn Qián, Mí Zhú, {\i0}and {\i1}Jiǎn Yōng{\i0}, and generals {\i1}Yúncháng, Yìdé, {\i0}and {\i1}Zǐlóng.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}They all completely support each other, \Nhow could you not count them as sage men?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Sir, why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Guan Yu, Zhang Fei, Zhao Yun are warriors rivaling of ten-thousand men.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}But its pitiable that they aren't made more use of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Sun Qian, Jian Yong, \Nand Mi Zhu are inexpert literati —
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1043.182)}{\bord14.318} — Not men of grand strategies and statesmanship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1043.182)}{\bord14.318}Teacher, your words are most correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}I have searched for such able men before —
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}— but haven't had the chance to meet a man of such talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}Xuande, is it not like how Confucius once said:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318\i1}"Within a township of ten families, \Nyou will find one who is venerable and virtuous."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}Why claim there are no men of talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}Forgive my ignorance on this matter. I'd like to ask your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}The great heroes and prodigies of today are already here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318\pos(726.136,1002.273)}Sir Xuande must go inquire them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318\pos(726.136,1002.273)}I wish to know who these prodigies are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:06:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.318\i1\pos(720,1034)}'Sleeping Dragon'{\i0} and{\i1} 'Fledgling Phoenix'{\i0}\N With even one by your side, peace can be brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}Please explain sir, who are these\N {\i1}Sleeping Dragon {\i0}and{\i1}Fledgling Phoenix?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,General, feel free to stay overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be time to talk again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:38.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The reason why you haven't yet accomplished your great undertaking —
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:43.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318} — is because there are no virtuous sage men around to assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:53.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Dragon and Fledgling Phoenix... \NWith even one by your side, peace can be brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:03.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Zhao Yun unsuccessfully searched for Liu Bei outside Xiāngyáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:08.62,Thinking,,0,0,0,,When he saw water prints from the east of the Tán-Creek to the west —
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:13.64,Thinking,,0,0,0,,— he figured Liu Bei came back to Xinye, and returned there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:18.10,Thinking,,0,0,0,,However, even after he returned to Xinye, he couldn't find Liu Bei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.00,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Zhao Yun felt very worried  —
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:23.54,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318} — so he searched the entire western bank of the Tán-Creek.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:28.65,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}At Shuijing Mountain, he met Liu Bei, and the two headed back for Xinye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:34.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}Along the way, they found a man seeking to serve them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:50.00,chs,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}{\i1}...there is a wise man on the mountain, hoping to find a lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:10:02.50,chs,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}{\i1} The lord seeks wise advisors,\N but still he has no clue!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"The lord seeks wise advisers..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"... But still he has no clue."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong, could that man be either \NSleeping Dragon or Fledging Phoenix?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask where you came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,From all around the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask for your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I am from Yǐngshàng. My name is {\i1}Shàn Fú.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you are recruiting men of talent for your cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you listened to my melody, \Nyou have earned my respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you, sir, for not refusing me.\NYou have my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, let us discuss this at a hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:43.70,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,500,5500,5700)\pos(331.461,670)\bord16}Shàn Fú \N(AKA. Xú Shù \NStyled, Yuánzhí)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That horse must be 'Dilu'!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Although this horse can run a 1,000 li,\N it will bring misfortune to its rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, do not ride it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This horse galloped across the Tán-Creek!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How can it bring misfotune?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This horse will curse its rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a way to avoid this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, if you have someone in mind you detest, \Nyou should give this horse to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the curse take effect, and then reclaim it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No more problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I happened to hear your melody. It was out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at you, you seemed to be a man of talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I hoped you would help me achieve my ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet instead of showing me the way, \Nyou talk of causing petty harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you may need to find someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have long heard of your benevolent reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'm shown it was not empty talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Shan Fu, am willing to follow you to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I call myself benevolent! \NI only wish to seek your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, don't be too humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of Xinye have sung this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16\i1}"Xinye's Lord, Uncle Liu, \Nblessed is land, where he would stand."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your benevolence, \Nthe people placed great faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to appoint you as our {\i1}Army-Strategist{\i0}, \Nfor you to train them to achieve great things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the 5th year of the Jian'an era.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I raised a righteous army to destroy each menace of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I defeated Yuan Shao and retook four provinces!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have pacified the Wuhuan-tribes and appeased Liaodong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, with the north pacified, I will again march my army!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:44.43,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Jīng-Xiāng (荆襄)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I will first take the lands of {\i1}Jīng-Xiāng{\i0}, \Nthen conquer Eastern Wú!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei had tried earlier to take the capital of Xǔ (Xǔchāng).
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We must kill him while his wings have \Nnot developed to eliminate a future problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Generals, heed my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Rén.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:14:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:14:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lǐ Diǎn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lü Kuàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lü Xiáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of you will advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:11.78,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,200,5900,200)\pos(260.015,706.427)}Cáo Cāo\NStyled: Mèngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead 30,000 troops to garrison at \N{\i1}Fánchéng{\i0}, and scout Liu Biao's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Disperse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We should speed up preparations to garrison Fancheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,General Cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei has garrisoned at Xinye, \Nbuilding up his armies and supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This suggests he will take Xǔdū.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He is getting too bold. \NWe must eliminate him early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:47.84,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,5800,6500)\pos(243.169,526.356)}Lü Kuàng
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:47.84,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,5800,6500)\pos(687.588,481.447)}Lü Xiáng
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we brothers joined the Chancellor, we haven't had great achievements —
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,, — yet still receive the Chancellor's patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we're going to Fancheng, we ask of 5,000 elite soldiers —
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,, —  to seize Liu Bei's head and \Ngift it to the Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! I will let you two \Nlead the elite troops towards Xinye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:06.60,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,490,8150,2620)\pos(1227.792,718.141)}Cáo Rén\NStyled: Zǐxiào
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei will be first to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother! Strategist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How could that Lü Kuang \Nand Lü Xiang be a match against us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:28.72,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,5000,5420)\pos(217.133,744.083)}Zhāng Fēi\NStyled: Yìdé
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong and I cut them down in two rounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! You may sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, your plan was ingenious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Cao wants Lü Kuang and \NLü Xiang to intrude upon our Xinye —
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,, — but with only a single plan from our Strategist, \Nhe has now lost two of his warrior-generals!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,However, how can Cao Cao be willing to concede at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Xinye has just a few soldiers. \NHow can we counter the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry, my lord-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:17:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Report! A large army led by Cao Ren and \NLi Dian is coming towards Xinye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we defeated Lü Kuang and Lü Xiang —
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,— a furious Cao Ren led his entire army over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fancheng must be empty then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We must use this chance to take it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Guan Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhang Fei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you will lead thousand soldiers to meet the enemy at Fancheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Two generals just need to follow my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, with their departure, \Nhow can we defend ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We will guard Xinye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhao Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong, you will accompany us and await our command.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:38.82,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,4000,4420)\pos(1193.071,692.265)}Cáo Rén\NStyled: Zǐxiào
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Li Dian is defeated! Signal the men to finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Heed my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Change formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, why are you halting our attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the {\i1}Golden Locks of Eight Gates Formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong rushed into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you, Zilong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When I rushed into their formation, a cloud of smoke rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find that Li Dian!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cao army changed formation, encasing me in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,With much effort, I broke out,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and my other troops didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,By the look of it, that formation is hard to break through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Golden Locks of Eight Gates Formation has eight regiments and gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They are tightly linked together without even a gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If our troops rushed into them, \Nyou will fight a different soldier each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The formation has the soldiers intersect with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The formation never stops turning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They can hit you, but you cannot hit them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If a soldier joins them, it will grow the cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how brave your soldiers are, \Nthey'll eventually lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.15,0:22:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the strength of this formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, is there no plan that can defeat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Although they are grouped neatly —
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.65,0:22:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,, — they lack a Supreme Ultimate, \Ntheir center has no commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,General, enter through the Southeast corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.75,0:22:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you attack the Western Gate, they will rout.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.42,0:22:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.78,0:23:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Have your men maintain their flanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass the order!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.85,0:25:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We have broken through them!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.26,0:25:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pursue them!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.80,0:25:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you are extraordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.20,0:25:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, you flatter me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.96,0:25:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You should order our troops not to\N pursue them, but to remain at camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.62,0:25:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.36,0:25:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he break through our formation?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.00,0:25:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We will raid Liu Bei's camp tonight \Nwhile he's complacent from victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.40,0:25:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We will succeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.06,0:25:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,General Cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.98,0:25:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be sage men helping Liu Bei now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.20,0:26:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that our army is at this point, \Nwe must defend Fancheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.41,0:26:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We will fall back if we don't succeed tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.82,0:26:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! Liu Bei must have prepared for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.62,0:26:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Armies aren't run by paranoia!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.57,0:26:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.59,0:26:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.20,0:26:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been outmaneuvered!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.06,0:26:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.80,0:27:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.03,0:27:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.13,0:27:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Find a ferry!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.00,0:27:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Find a ferry!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.15,0:27:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Ren, halt! I've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.64,0:27:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.69,0:27:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.61,0:28:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the gates! Cao Ren's army has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.82,0:28:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the gates! Cao Ren's army has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.94,0:28:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Ren's army has returned! Open the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.86,0:28:34.48,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,5500,5820)\pos(1228.993,727.447)}Guān Yǔ\NStyled: Yúncháng
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.06,0:28:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Ren, you boor! We already captured Fancheng!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.43,0:28:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.10,0:28:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come! Let us drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.50,0:29:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Strategist, thank you! Thank you, elder brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.07,0:29:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.07,0:29:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.68,0:29:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since this gentleman has joined us, \Nwe've been victorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.25,0:29:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I always knew if I were to achieve my undertaking —
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.34,0:29:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,, — I would have to have sage, talented men like him by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.36,0:29:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct, correct, correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.80,0:29:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you have my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.55,0:29:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.40,0:29:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, you flatter me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.78,0:29:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, you graced me with your patronage. \NI am merely repaying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.67,0:30:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare not receive such respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.85,0:30:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With this gentleman's assistance, we will persevere! Soon our great cause can be realized!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.74,0:30:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Another round!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.08,0:30:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.75,0:30:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We wish Your Lordship great fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.33,0:30:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.36,0:30:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, we lost Fancheng!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.43,0:30:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You may punish us!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.81,0:30:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pride led you to ignore warnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.52,0:30:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus you were defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.72,0:30:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,However, because of your past achievements, I shall spare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.50,0:30:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We thank you for your mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.50,0:30:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet not too long ago, Liu Bei was handily defeated at Rǔnán under my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.40,0:30:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you get routed whenever you attack Xinye.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.52,0:30:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the Golden Locks \Nof Eight Gates Formation has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.16,0:31:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei must have received a great talent to his ranks, planning his next maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.81,0:31:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.78,0:31:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard that Liu Bei has gained a judicious advisor called Shan Fu.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.70,0:31:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the one who broke our formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.00,0:31:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shan Fu? What is he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.30,0:31:33.74,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\bord7\fade(255,0,255,0,500,6500,6900)\pos(249.346,760)} Chéng Yù \NStyled, Zhòngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.85,0:31:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, Shan Fu is a fake name.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.17,0:31:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He is actually a man from Yingshang, by the name of {\i1}Xú Shù{\i0}, styled {\i1}Yuánzhí.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.32,0:31:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was young, he practiced swordsmanship
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.21,0:31:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a forthright personality, and likes to fight against injustice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.88,0:31:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Near the end of the Zhōngpíng era, he killed a corrupt official to avenge a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.88,0:31:49.24,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Zhōngpíng(中平) = 184-189 CE, last calendar era of Emperor Líng of Hàn
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.72,0:31:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he had no choice but to go into hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.13,0:31:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was arrested, \Nhe was asked for his name, but did not reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.40,0:32:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The officials tied him to a cart \Nand drummed in the streets to learn about his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.10,0:32:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,However, because of his heroic deeds, no one identified him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.38,0:32:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The office could only put him in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.28,0:32:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Later however, there was 'someone' who freed him
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.92,0:32:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Xu Shu then changed his name, \Nand has since he devoted himself to learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.74,0:32:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He visited famous teachers and \Nbecame enriched with knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.11,0:32:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He often meets with people like Sima Hui about the current state of the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.40,0:32:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How does Xu Shu's talent compare to yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.63,0:32:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten times as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.72,0:32:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pity! What a pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.75,0:32:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Another talented man falls under Liu Bei's palms.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.09,0:33:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that his wings are fully developed, how can I not be concerned?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.48,0:33:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Although Xu Shu serves under Liu Bei —
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.17,0:33:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,, — if you want him under your command, it can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.51,0:33:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you suggesting, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.91,0:33:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Xu Shu is a filial man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.24,0:33:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When he lost his father, only his mother stayed in the household.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.25,0:33:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When his brother Xu Kang passed away, their mother had no one to support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.39,0:33:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, you should invite her over to Xudu  —
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.42,0:33:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,, — and have her summon her son with a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.76,0:33:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Xu Shu will certainly come!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.00,0:33:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.20,0:33:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Send someone to Yingchuan right away, \Nand bring Xu Shu's mother here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.84,0:33:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you make me come to Xudu?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.20,0:33:54.84,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(509.633,517.72)}Mother of Xu Shu
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.18,0:33:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.00,0:34:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that your son, Xu Yuanzhi, is a prodigy of our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.79,0:34:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he is assisting that rebel Liu Bei \Nin undermining the Imperial Court from Xinye.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.10,0:34:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it not pitiful that such a\Nbeautiful jade fell into the mud?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.70,0:34:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you to come here in order for you to return him back to Xudu.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.37,0:34:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can petition the Emperor to grant you a hefty reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.39,0:34:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.53,0:34:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of man is Liu Bei?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.84,0:34:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A lesser man from Zhuo Commandery who claims to be the Emperor's uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.65,0:34:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Treacherous to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.82,0:34:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As they say; A crook in gentleman's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.51,0:34:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you lying to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.51,0:35:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that Liu Xuande is a descendant of the Prince Jìng of Zhōngshān —
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.65,0:35:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,— and of Emperor Jǐng of Hàn's lineage.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.85,0:35:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He treats the virtuous with the utmost respect and has built up a righteous reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.33,0:35:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a hero of this age!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.06,0:35:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My son is blessed to have such sagacious lord to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.73,0:35:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the Chancellor of the Hàn in name only, because you are its traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.50,0:35:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You lie about Liu Xuande being a rebel to have my son turn away from the light into darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.88,0:35:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you no shame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.74,0:35:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Out with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.80,0:35:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.04,0:35:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Behead her!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.66,0:35:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypocrite!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.06,0:35:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop the execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.20,0:35:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Xu Shu's mother has angered you to have herself executed —
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.66,0:35:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,— for if you kill her, it will only worsen your reputation and instead make her a martyr.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.95,0:36:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,By killing her, Xu Shu will either commit suicide or he will devote himself to Liu Bei to avenge her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.65,0:36:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to let her live, so that Xu Shu would be split between two.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.02,0:36:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he stays with Liu Bei, he won't be as dedicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.56,0:36:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Xu Shu's mother remain here, for I have yet another plan to make Xu Shu come.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.72,0:36:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,True. I shall send Xu Shu's mother somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.74,0:36:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.24,0:36:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, how have you been lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.14,0:36:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Cheng, you brought me something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.16,0:36:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.40,0:37:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When Yuanzhi and I studied together, we were like brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.78,0:37:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus ma'am, you are like a mother to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.90,0:37:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,However, now that Yuanzhi is not here for you, \NI will be for you in his stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.45,0:37:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Cheng, you are a kind man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.79,0:37:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, you have submitted to Cao Cao. How-
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.72,0:37:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, you needn't say more.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.90,0:37:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fates are unkind, it is how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.53,0:37:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When I get the chance, I will send you back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.10,0:37:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.40,0:37:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.64,0:37:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to do, so I'm afraid I cannot stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.08,0:37:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.10,0:37:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.65,0:37:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.54,0:37:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.26,0:37:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.00,0:38:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Cheng left you another letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.73,0:38:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheng Yu really is a scholarly gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.87,0:38:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I already have his letter, so I should reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.62,0:38:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fetch me the pen and inkstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.98,0:38:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.94,0:39:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My lord, someone from Xudu is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.11,0:39:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He was asking where Shan Fu was, he had something to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.14,0:39:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.12,0:39:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I am a servant of Ma'am Xu!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.12,0:39:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have here a letter by her own hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.38,0:39:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.55,0:40:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, what is it that has you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.02,0:40:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.84,0:40:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, say what it is. Don't be so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.28,0:40:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.30,0:40:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My real name is {\i1}Xú Shù, {\i0}styled{\i1} Yuánzhí,{\i0} from Yingchuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.26,0:40:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went into hiding,\N I changed my name to Shan Fu.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.40,0:40:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Liu Jingsheng was \Nseeking advisers, so I visited him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.34,0:40:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In discussing matters, I came to learn that he was useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.34,0:41:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I left a letter of resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.81,0:41:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Overnight, I stayed with Master Sima Water-Mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.76,0:41:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Master criticized me for not recognizing \Na sagacious lord, so he recommended you to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.55,0:41:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was lucky to have your favor and use of my talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.16,0:41:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But for this, now Cao Cao targets me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.52,0:41:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, my mother is now imprisoned in Xudu, under Cao Cao's torment.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.48,0:41:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother's letter tells thus. I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.25,0:41:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that I do not wish to serve you —
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.59,0:41:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,— but my mother suffers in chains!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.96,0:41:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I must leave for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.04,0:42:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.48,0:42:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Love between mother and child is the most innate of all. Yuanzhi, you shouldn't consider me before her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.15,0:42:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After you meet with your mother, \Nit will not be too late to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.39,0:42:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.83,0:42:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuanzhi, no need to leave just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.33,0:42:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I implore you to stay with me just this night!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.40,0:42:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I will bid you farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.30,0:42:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, I-!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.71,0:42:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuanzhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.78,0:42:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.44,0:42:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Xu Shu takes his leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.64,0:42:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.63,0:43:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.72,0:43:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuanzhi is a rare genius in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.55,0:43:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he saw the ins and outs of our army in Xinye.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.31,0:43:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If he goes to Cao Cao, his knowledge will be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.60,0:43:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That would bear ill toward us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.68,0:43:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, you should persist. Do not let him leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.85,0:43:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Cao will see Yuanzhi did not join him, so he'll kill his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.45,0:43:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When Yuanzhi hears of this, \Nhe will certainly desire vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.92,0:43:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.62,0:43:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}To kill a mother \Nto keep the son, is atrocity!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.72,0:43:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Forcing him to stay —
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.58,0:43:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318} — to sever the bond of \Nmother and son, is depravity!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.58,0:43:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}I would rather die than become vile!
